2B479923.Line7.F52ED: W-who are you!? Leave me alone!

34457CE6.VoiceDir9.F53E7: Attempting to explain a situation but also calm a young girl getting herself worked up liable to hurt herself.

40528148.Line17.F53E7: Questions later. First, drink this before you drop dead from your short-sighted brew.

5D6A2C9D.Line1.F52ED: (coughing) No, but it's the only way I can go home again...

66680C4C.VoiceDir3.F52ED: Terrified. You just drank poison hoping it would cure you, but you might drop dead right here and now.

727514C2.Line11.F53E7: Of course it hurts, you drank boiled poison.

9088AD15.VoiceDir17.F53E7: Matter of fact, urgent but not without care. You want this girl to be okay.

9A50FF50.VoiceDir7.F52ED: Terrified. A blood-soaked strange woman is walking towards you.

C2AB408F.VoiceDir11.F53E7: Strong, straight to the point but hiding slight bemusement at the situation.

C53C16B9.Line9.F53E7: Your blood is enflamed. Close your eyes and breathe slowly.

CC7392CA.VoiceDir1.F52ED: Nervous but determined. The only thing that matters is going back home again.

F6942F7F.VoiceDir15.F52ED: How did this strange woman stop your curse from manifesting?
